Reasoning: The paper discusses the expressiveness and machine processability of different types of Knowledge Organization Systems (KOS) in the context of the semantic web. This involves natural language processing techniques and a comparative analysis of different KOS, which are all relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), deep learning (cs.DL), and databases (cs.DB).
